{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-tsx","path":"/algorithm/boat/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/boat/"},"html":"<p><a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42885\"><img src=\"./images/boat.jpg\" alt=\"문제 설명\"></a></p>\n<h2>접근방법</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">people</code> 배열을 <code class=\"language-text\">정렬</code> 해준다. <code class=\"language-text\">가장 무거운 사람, 가장 가벼운 사람을 사용 하기 위해서</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>가장 무거운 사람 + 가장 가벼운 사람 이 배의 무게 제한보다 크다면,</li>\n<li>가장 무거운 사람만 빼버린다.</li>\n<li>가장 무거운 사람 + 가장 가벼운 사람 이 배의 무게 제한보다 작거나 같다면,</li>\n<li>가장 무거운 사람, 가장 가벼운 사람 둘다 뺀다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>시간초과(프로그램)를 막기위해서 배열을 직접 건들지 않고 index pointer를 2개 사용한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>가장 무거운 사람의 위치 => <code class=\"language-text\">big</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>가장 무거운 사람이 빠져야 하면 big =- 1 </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>가장 가벼운 사람의 위치 => <code class=\"language-text\">small</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>가장 가벼운 사람이 빠져야 하면 smail += 1</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>small 값이 big 값보다 크게 되면 반복문을 중지한다. (모든 사람이 다 빠져나갔음을 의미한다.)</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-py line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>people<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> limit<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    people<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sort<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    small <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    big <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>people<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> small <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> big<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>people<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> people<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>small<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> people<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>big<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> limit<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            small <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n            big <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            big <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\n        count <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> count</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스 LV2] 구명 보트","tags":["파이썬","알고리즘","algorithm","python"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/boat/","next":"/algorithm/bad-user/","nextTitle":"[프로그래머스 LV3] 불량 사용자","previous":"/algorithm/124/","previousTitle":"[프로그래머스 LV2] 124 나라의 숫자"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3501822393"]}